ECT & PERSON</p>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\"><a class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink-small\" href=\"../recruit/interview_project1/\">PROJECT</a></li>\r\n                <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\"><a class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink-small\" href=\"../recruit/interview_person1/\">PERSON 1</a></li>\r\n                <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\"><a class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink-small\" href=\"../recruit/interview_person2/\">PERSON 2</a></li>\r\n                <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\"><a class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink-small\" href=\"../recruit/interview_person3/\">PERSON 3</a></li>\r\n                <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\"> <a class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink\" href=\"../recruit/graduate/\">募集要項</a></li>\r\n                <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\"> <a class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink\" href=\"../recruit/faq/\">よくある質問</a></li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n            </li>\r\n            <li class=\"siteHeader__listItem\"> <a class=\"siteHeader__listItemLink\" href=\"../topics/\">トピックス</a></li>\r\n            <li class=\"siteHeader__listItem\"> <a class=\"siteHeader__listItemLink\" href=\"../information_disclosure/\">情報公開</a></li>\r\n          </ul>\r\n          <div class=\"siteHeader__contactBox\"> <a class=\"siteHeader__contactLink\" href=\"../inquiry/\">お問い合わせ</a></div>\r\n        </nav>\r\n        <nav class=\"siteHeader__nav-sp\" role=\"navigation\">\r\n          <div class=\"siteHeader__navInner-sp js-humContent\">\r\n            <div class=\"siteHeader__closeBtnBox js-humCloseBtn\"><span class=\"siteHeader__closeBtn\"></span></div>\r\n            <div class=\"siteHeader__list\"> \r\n              <div class=\"siteHeader__listItem\"> <a class=\"siteHeader__listItemLink-sp\" href=\"../\"><span class=\"siteHeader__listItemLinkTitle\">トップへ戻る</span><span class=\"siteHeader__listItemLinkSubText\">TOP</span></a></div>\r\n              <div class=\"siteHeader__listItem\">\r\n                <div class=\"siteHeader__listItemPlusBox js-puls\"><a class=\"siteHeader__listItemLink\" href=\"../business/\">事業紹介<span class=\"siteHeader__listItemLinkSubText\">BUSINESS</span></a></div>\r\n              </div>\r\n              <div class=\"siteHeader__listItem\"> \r\n                <div class=\"siteHeader__listItemPlusBox js-puls\"><a class=\"siteHeader__listItemLink\" href=\"../company/\">会社情報<span class=\"siteHeader__listItemLinkSubText\">CORPORATE</span></a><span class=\"siteHeader__pulsBtn\"></span></div>\r\n                <ul class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenu js-content\">\r\n                  <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\"> <a class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink\" href=\"../company/profile/\">会社概要</a></li>\r\n                  <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\"> <a class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink\" href=\"../company/greeting/\">社長挨拶</a></li>\r\n                  <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\"> <a class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink\" href=\"../company/history/\">沿革</a></li>\r\n                  <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\"> <a class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink\" href=\"../company/philosophy/\">企業理念</a></li>\r\n                <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\"> <a class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink\" href=\"../company/purpose/\">パーパス</a></li>\r\n                  <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\"> <a class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink\" href=\"../company/quality/\">品質 ・ 環境方針</a></li>\r\n                  <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\"> <a class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink\" href=\"../company/health/\">健康経営</a></li>\r\n                  <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\"> <a class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink\" href=\"../company/organization/\">組織図</a></li>\r\n                  <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\"> <a class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink\" href=\"../company/office/\">拠点一覧</a></li>\r\n                </ul>\r\n              </div>\r\n              <div class=\"siteHeader__listItem\"> \r\n                <div class=\"siteHeader__listItemPlusBox js-puls\"><a class=\"siteHeader__listItemLink\" href=\"../recruit/\">採用情報<span class=\"siteHeader__listItemLinkSubText\">RECRUIT</span></a><span class=\"siteHeader__pulsBtn\"></span></div>\r\n                <ul class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenu js-content\">\r\n                  <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\"> <a class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink\" href=\"../recruit/facilities/\">JETがつくるもの・仕事の流れ</a></li>\r\n                  <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\"> <a class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink\" href=\"../recruit/workstyle/\">JETの働き方</a></li>\r\n                  <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\">\r\n                    <p class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink-nolink\">PROJECT & PERSON</p>\r\n                  </li>\r\n                  <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\"><a class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink-small\" href=\"../recruit/interview_project1/\">PROJECT</a></li>\r\n                  <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\"><a class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink-small\" href=\"../recruit/interview_person1/\">PERSON 1</a></li>\r\n                  <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\"><a class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink-small\" href=\"../recruit/interview_person2/\">PERSON 2</a></li>\r\n                  <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\"><a class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink-small\" href=\"../recruit/interview_person3/\">PERSON 3</a></li>\r\n                  <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\"> <a class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink\" href=\"../recruit/graduate/\">募集要項</a></li>\r\n                  <li class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuItem\"> <a class=\"siteHeader__listContentMenuLink\" href=\"../recruit/faq/\">よくある質問</a></li>\r\n                </ul>\r\n              </div>\r\n              <div class=\"siteHeader__listItem\"> <a class=\"siteHeader__listItemLink-sp\" href=\"../topics/\"><span class=\"siteHeader__listItemLinkTitle\">トピックス</span><span class=\"siteHeader__listItemLinkSubText\">TOPICS</span></a></div>\r\n              <div class=\"siteHeader__listItem\"> <a class=\"siteHeader__listItemLink-sp\" href=\"../information_disclosure/\"><span class=\"siteHeader__listItemLinkTitle\">情報公開</span><span class=\"siteHeader__listItemLinkSubText\">INFORMATION DISCLOSURE</span></a></div>\r\n              <div class=\"siteHeader__listItem siteHeader__listItem-contact\"> <a class=\"siteHeader__listItemLink-sp\" href=\"../inquiry/\"><span class=\"siteHeader__listItemLinkTitle\">お問い合わせ</span><span class=\"siteHeader__listItemLinkSubText\">CONTACT</span></a></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </nav>\r\n        <div class=\"siteHeader__humMenu js-humOpenBtn\"><span class=\"siteHeader__humMenuLine siteHeader__humMenuLine-first\"> </span><span class=\"siteHeader__humMenuLine siteHeader__humMenuLine-second\">  </span><span class=\"siteHeader__humMenuLine siteHeader__humMenuLine-third\">  </span></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </header>\r\n    <main class=\"main\" role=\"main\">\r\n      <div class=\"recruit\">\r\n        <div class=\"recruit__wrap\">\r\n          <div class=\"recruit__inner\">\r\n            <div class=\"c-breadcrumb\">\r\n              <ul class=\"c-breadcrumb__list\"> \r\n                <li class=\"c-breadcrumb__listItem\"> <a class=\"c-breadcrumb__listItemLink\" href=\"../\"><img class=\"c-breadcrumb__listItemHome\" src=\"../_assets/images/common/icon_home.png\" alt=\"ホーム\"></a></li>\r\n                <li class=\"c-breadcrumb__listItem\"> <span class=\"c-breadcrumb__listItemText\">採用情報（トップ）</span></li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"c-pageTitle\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"> \r\n              <h1 class=\"c-decorativeTitle-blue c-pageTitle__heading\">RECRUIT </h1>\r\n              <h2 class=\"c-heading-blue c-pageTitle__text\">採用情報</h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"recruit__content\">\r\n              <section class=\"recruit__sec\">\r\n                <div class=\"recruit__headingDescBox\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"> \r\n                  <p class=\"recruit__headingDescTitle\">求む、<br class=\"u-spDb\">「環境へのひたむきな思い」<br class=\"u-spDb\">×「熱い挑戦心」</p>\r\n                  <p class=\"recruit__headingDesc\">当社の社風は「実直で真面目」。</p>\r\n                  <p class=\"recruit__headingDesc\">決して器用に立ち回るのは得意ではないけれど、地に足をつけて着実に、そして真摯に<br class=\"u-pcDb\">取り組むことで確かな実績と信頼を築いてきました。</p>\r\n                  <p class=\"recruit__headingDesc\">何より社員一人ひとりが、その実直さ・誠実さの下に環境への熱い思いを秘めています。</p>\r\n                  <p class=\"recruit__headingDesc\">私たちは、前身となった企業から受け継いだ「挑戦するDNA」を呼び覚まし、<br class=\"u-pcDb\">共に果敢にチャレンジする気概を持った仲間を求めています。</p>\r\n                  <p class=\"recruit__headingDesc\">あなたの「環境への思い」×「挑戦心」を、JFE環境テクノロジーで発揮しませんか。</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"recruit__valueBox\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"> \r\n                  <div class=\"recruit__valueTitleBox\"><span class=\"c-decorativeSmallTitle-blue recruit__valueTItle-en\">VALUE </span>\r\n                    <h3 class=\"recruit__valueTitle-first\">JFE環境テクノロジーが<br class=\"u-spDb\">提供する価値</h3>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <div class=\"recruit__valueDescBox u-spDb\">\r\n                    <div class=\"recruit__valueDesc\">私たちの仕事そのものが、<br class=\"u-spDb\">持続可能な社会を支え、必要とされる</div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <div class=\"recruit__valueImgBox\"><img class=\"recruit__valueImg u-pcDb\" src=\"../_assets/images/lower/recruit/recruit_value01.png\" alt=\"JFE環境テクノロジーが提供する価値\"><img class=\"recruit__valueImg u-spDb\" src=\"../_assets/images/lower/recruit/recruit_value01-sp.png\" alt=\"JFE環境テクノロジーが提供する価値\"></div>\r\n                  <div class=\"recruit__valueImgUnderBox u-spDb\">\r\n                    <p class=\"recruit__valueImgUnderBoxTitle\">エンジニアリング</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"recruit__valueImgUnderBoxText\">エンジニアリングとは知恵と技術を結集し、<br>独創性あるものをつくりだすことです。<br>清掃工場といった環境プラントを<br>創造（設計）し、つくる（建設）ことが<br>私たちのエンジニアリングです。<br>わたしたちがつくるプラントは持続可能な<br>社会には無くてはならないものです。</p>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <div class=\"recruit__valueImgUnderBoxGr u-spDb\">\r\n                    <p class=\"recruit__valueImgUnderBoxTitle gr\">O&M</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"recruit__valueImgUnderBoxText\">優れたプラントや施設をつくっても、<br>十分に能力を発揮できなければ意味がありません。<br>当社はおよそ40年の実績を持つ運転・<br>維持管理（O＆M）で施設の能力を最大限発揮させ、<br>安全・安定稼働を担います。</p>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <div class=\"recruit__valueDescBox u-pcDb\">\r\n                    <div class=\"recruit__valueDesc\">私たちの仕事そのものが、持続可能な社会を支え、必要とされる</div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"recruit__checkBoxWrap\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"> \r\n                  <div class=\"recruit__checkBox\">\r\n                    <div class=\"recruit__checkTitleBox\"> <span class=\"recruit__checkTitle-sub\"> <span class=\"recruit__checkTitle-sub-bold\">J</span>FE <span class=\"recruit__checkTitle-sub-bold\">E</span>nvironment <span class=\"recruit__checkTitle-sub-bold\">T</span>echnology Company, Limited</span>\r\n                      <h3 class=\"recruit__checkTitle\">JETをもっと知る</h3>\r\n                      <spna class=\"recruit__checkText\">CHECK!</spna>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <ul class=\"recruit__checkImgList\">\r\n                      <li class=\"recruit__checkImgListItem\"><a class=\"recruit__checkImgListItemLink\" href=\"../recruit/facilities/\"> \r\n                          <figrue class=\"recruit__facilitiesListImgBox\"> <img class=\"recruit__facilitiesListImg\" src=\"../_assets/images/lower/recruit/recruit_img01.jpg\" alt=\"JETがつくるもの・仕事の流れ\"></figrue>\r\n                          <div class=\"recruit__facilitiesListTextBox\"> <span class=\"recruit__facilitiesListText\">JETがつくるもの・仕事の流れ </span></div></a></li>\r\n                      <li class=\"recruit__checkImgBoxListItem\"><a class=\"recruit__checkImgListItemLink\" href=\"../recruit/workstyle/\">\r\n                          <figrue class=\"recruit__facilitiesListImgBox\"> <img class=\"recruit__facilitiesListImg\" src=\"../_assets/images/lower/recruit/recruit_img02.jpg\" alt=\"JETの働き方\"></figrue>\r\n                          <div class=\"recruit__facilitiesListTextBox\"> <span class=\"recruit__facilitiesListText\">JETの働き方 </span></div></a></li>\r\n                    </ul>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"recruit__plantWrap\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\r\n                  <div class=\"recruit__plantBox\"> \r\n                    <div class=\"recruit__plantTitleBox\"> \r\n                      <p class=\"recruit__plantTitle\">日本有数の企業グループ「ＪＦＥグループ」のプラント会社</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"recruit__plantContent\"> \r\n                      <div class=\"recruit__plantTextArea\">\r\n                        <p class=\"recruit__plantText\">JFEグループは鉄の製造を中核に６万人を超える従業員を擁する企業グループ。その事業領域は人々の安全で快適なくらしを支えるエンジニアリング事業に及びます。私たちはJFEエンジニアリングのもと、環境プラントを通じて持続可能な循環型社会実現のため、技術で支え、ひたむきに歩んでまいります。</p><span class=\"recruit__plantText-small\">※2022年3月末現在64,295人（連結ベース、<br>　JFEホールディングス株式会社公表による）</span>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div class=\"recruit__plantImgArea\">\r\n                        <figure class=\"recruit__plantImgBox\"> <img class=\"recruit__plantImg u-pcDb\" src=\"../_assets/images/lower/recruit/recruit_img03.png\" alt=\"日本有数の企業グループ「ＪＦＥグループ」のプラント会社\"><img class=\"recruit__plantImg u-spDb\" src=\"../_assets/images/lower/recruit/recruit_img03-sp.jpg\" alt=\"日本有数の企業グループ「ＪＦＥグループ」のプラント会社\"></figure>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </section>\r\n              <section class=\"recruit__sec u-pcDb\">\r\n                <div class=\"recruit__projectWrap\">\r\n                  <div class=\"recruit__projectInner\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"> \r\n                    <div class=\"recruit__projectTitleBox\">\r\n                      <h3 class=\"recruit__projectTitle\">PROJECT & <b class=\"u-spDb\"> </b>PERSON</h3>\r\n                      <h3 class=\"recruit__projectSubTitle\">〜プロジェクトに挑む先輩社員の声〜 </h3><span class=\"recruit__projectTitle-en c-decorativeSmallTitle-whiteTranparent\">INTERVIEW </span>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"recruit__projectContent\">\r\n                      <div class=\"recruit__projectTextArea\"> \r\n                        <div class=\"recruit__projectDescBox\"> \r\n                          <p class=\"recruit__projectDesc\">各地で展開する多種多様なプロジェクト。</p>\r\n                          <p class=\"recruit__projectDesc\">その中で、当社の社員たちはどんな想いを胸に取り組み、<br>苦労や困難を乗り越えて成長の礎としているのでしょうか。</p>\r\n                          <p class=\"recruit__projectDesc\">各プロジェクトの担当メンバーに、その案件を通じて得たもの、<br>当時の印象的なエピソード、プロジェクトでの経験を礎として<br>見据える自身の未来について語っていただきました。</p>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"recruit__projectBtnBox\"> \r\n                          <p class=\"recruit__projectBtnTitle\">PROJECT</p>\r\n                          <ul class=\"recruit__projectBtnList\">\r\n                            <li class=\"recruit__projectBtnListItem\" id=\"recruit-hoverBlue01\"><a class=\"recruit__projectBtnLink blue\" href=\"../recruit/interview_project1/\">\r\n                                <div class=\"recruit__projectBtnNumBox\"> \r\n                                  <p class=\"recruit__projectBtnNum\">1</p>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div class=\"recruit__projectBtnTextBox\"> \r\n                                  <p class=\"recruit__projectBtnText\" id=\"projectBtnText01\">インフラを守り・強化し・次代につなぐ</p>\r\n                                </div></a></li>\r\n                          </ul>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"recruit__projectBtnBox\"> \r\n                          <p class=\"recruit__projectBtnTitle\">PERSON\r\n                            <ul class=\"recruit__projectBtnList-nomb\">\r\n                              <li class=\"recruit__projectBtnListItem\" id=\"recruit-hoverGreen01\"> <a class=\"recruit__projectBtnLink green\" href=\"../recruit/interview_person1/\">\r\n                                  <div class=\"recruit__projectBtnNumBox\"> \r\n                                    <p class=\"recruit__projectBtnNum\">1</p>\r\n                                  </div>\r\n                                  <div class=\"recruit__projectBtnTextBox\"> \r\n                                    <p class=\"recruit__projectBtnText\" id=\"projectBtnText03\">現場に育てられ、現場を担う</p>\r\n                                  </div></a></li>\r\n                              <li class=\"recruit__projectBtnListItem\" id=\"recruit-hoverGreen02\"><a class=\"recruit__projectBtnLink green\" href=\"../recruit/interview_person2/\">\r\n                                  <div class=\"recruit__projectBtnNumBox\"> \r\n                                    <p class=\"recruit__projectBtnNum\">2</p>\r\n                                  </div>\r\n                                  <div class=\"recruit__projectBtnTextBox\"> \r\n                                    <p class=\"recruit__projectBtnText\" id=\"projectBtnText04\">「予算策定」 目標達成への道筋を描く仕事</p>\r\n                                  </div></a></li>\r\n                              <li class=\"recruit__projectBtnListItem\" id=\"recruit-hoverGreen03\"><a class=\"recruit__projectBtnLink green\" href=\"../recruit/interview_person3/\">\r\n                                  <div class=\"recruit__projectBtnNumBox\"> \r\n                                    <p class=\"recruit__projectBtnNum\">3</p>\r\n                                  </div>\r\n                                  <div class=\"recruit__projectBtnTextBox\"> \r\n                                    <p class=\"recruit__projectBtnText\" id=\"projectBtnText05\">研究職から設計担当へ 育休を経て復帰</p>\r\n                                  </div></a></li>\r\n                            </ul>\r\n                          </p>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div class=\"recruit__projectImgArea\"> \r\n                        <figure class=\"recruit__projectImgBox recruit__projectImgBox-01 active\" id=\"projectImgPic-01\"> <img src=\"../_assets/images/lower/recruit/recruit_project01.jpg\" alt=\"インフラを守り・強化し・次代につなぐ\"></figure>\r\n                        <figure class=\"recruit__projectImgBox recruit__projectImgBox-02\" id=\"projectImgPic-02\"> <img src=\"../_assets/images/lower/recruit/recruit_project02.jpg\" alt=\"インフラを守り・強化し・次代につなぐ\"></figure>\r\n                        <figure class=\"recruit__projectImgBox recruit__projectImgBox-03\" id=\"projectImgPic-03\"> <img src=\"../_assets/images/lower/recruit/recruit_person01.jpg\" alt=\"インフラを守り・強化し・次代につなぐ\"></figure>\r\n                        <figure class=\"recruit__projectImgBox recruit__projectImgBox-04\" id=\"projectImgPic-04\"> <img src=\"../_assets/images/lower/recruit/recruit_person02.jpg\" alt=\"インフラを守り・強化し・次代につなぐ\"></figure>\r\n                        <figure class=\"recruit__projectImgBox recruit__projectImgBox-05\" id=\"projectImgPic-05\"> <img src=\"../_assets/images/lower/recruit/recruit_person03.jpg\" alt=\"インフラを守り・強化し・次代につなぐ\"></figure>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </section>\r\n              <section class=\"recruit__sec u-spDb\">\r\n                <div class=\"recruit__projectWrap\">\r\n                  <div class=\"recruit__projectInner\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"> \r\n                    <div class=\"recruit__projectTitleBox\">\r\n                      <h3 class=\"recruit__projectTitle\">PROJECT & <b class=\"u-spDb\"> </b>PERSON</h3>\r\n                      <h3 class=\"recruit__projectSubTitle\">〜プロジェクトに挑む先輩社員の声〜 </h3><span class=\"recruit__projectTitle-en c-decorativeSmallTitle-whiteTranparent\">INTERVIEW </span>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"recruit__projectContent\">\r\n                      <div class=\"recruit__projectTextArea\"> \r\n                        <div class=\"recruit__projectDescBox\"> \r\n                          <p class=\"recruit__projectDesc\">各地で展開する多種多様なプロジェクト。</p>\r\n                          <p class=\"recruit__projectDesc\">その中で、当社の社員たちはどんな想いを胸に取り組み、苦労や困難を乗り越えて成長の礎としているのでしょうか。</p>\r\n                          <p class=\"recruit__projectDesc\">各プロジェクトの担当メンバーに、その案件を通じて得たもの、当時の印象的なエピソード、プロジェクトでの経験を礎として見据える自身の未来について語っていただきました。</p>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <div class=\"swiper recruit__swiper\">\r\n                    <div class=\"swiper-container recruit__swiperContainer\">\r\n                      <ul class=\"swiper-wrapper recruit__swiperWrapper\">\r\n                        <li class=\"swiper-slide recruit__swiperSlide\">\r\n                          <figure class=\"recruit__slidePic\"> <img class=\"recruit__slideImg\" src=\"../_assets/images/lower/recruit/recruit_slide-01.jpg\" alt=\"PROJECT 1\"></figure>\r\n                          <div class=\"recruit__slideInner\">\r\n                            <p class=\"recruit__slideTitle\">PROJECT 1</p>\r\n                            <p class=\"recruit__slideSubTitle\">インフラを守り・強化し・次代につなぐ</p>\r\n                            <p class=\"recruit__slideText\">甲賀広域行政組合衛生センター<br>第2施設基幹的設備改良工事</p><a class=\"recruit__slideLink\" href=\"../recruit/interview_project1/\"> <span class=\"recruit__slideLinkText\">詳しく見る</span></a>\r\n                          </div>\r\n                        </li>\r\n                        <li class=\"swiper-slide recruit__swiperSlide\">\r\n                          <figure class=\"recruit__slidePic\"> <img class=\"recruit__slideImg\" src=\"../_assets/images/lower/recruit/recruit_slide-03.jpg\" alt=\"PEOPLE 1\"></figure>\r\n                          <div class=\"recruit__slideInner\">\r\n                            <p class=\"recruit__slideTitle\">PEOPLE 1</p>\r\n                            <p class=\"recruit__slideSubTitle\">現場に育てられ、現場を担う</p>\r\n                            <p class=\"recruit__slideText recruit__slideText-first\">豊橋市資源化センター</p><a class=\"recruit__slideLink\" href=\"../recruit/interview_person1/\"> <span class=\"recruit__slideLinkText\">詳しく見る</span></a>\r\n                          </div>\r\n                        </li>\r\n                        <li class=\"swiper-slide recruit__swiperSlide\">\r\n                          <figure class=\"recruit__slidePic\"> <img class=\"recruit__slideImg\" src=\"../_assets/images/lower/recruit/recruit_slide-04.jpg\" alt=\"PEOPLE 2\"></figure>\r\n                          <div class=\"recruit__slideInner\">\r\n                            <p class=\"recruit__slideTitle\">PEOPLE 2</p>\r\n                            <p class=\"recruit__slideSubTitle\">「予算策定」<br>目標達成への道筋を描く仕事</p>\r\n                            <p class=\"recruit__slideText recruit__slideText-second\">経営企画部</p><a class=\"recruit__slideLink\" href=\"../recruit/interview_person2/\"> <span class=\"recruit__slideLinkText\">詳しく見る</span></a>\r\n                          </div>\r\n                        </li>\r\n                        <li class=\"swiper-slide recruit__swiperSlide\">\r\n                          <figure class=\"recruit__slidePic\"> <img class=\"recruit__slideImg\" src=\"../_assets/images/lower/recruit/recruit_slide-05.jpg\" alt=\"PEOPLE 3\"></figure>\r\n                          <div class=\"recruit__slideInner\">\r\n                            <p class=\"recruit__slideTitle\">PEOPLE 3</p>\r\n                            <p class=\"recruit__slideSubTitle\">研究職から設計担当へ 育休を経て復帰</p>\r\n                            <p class=\"recruit__slideText recruit__slideText-first\">環境施設事業本部 設計部 基本計画課</p><a class=\"recruit__slideLink\" href=\"../recruit/interview_person3/\"> <span class=\"recruit__slideLinkText\">詳しく見る</span></a>\r\n                          </div>\r\n                        </li>\r\n                      </ul>\r\n                      <div class=\"navigation\"> \r\n                        <div class=\"navigation-prev swiper-button-prev\"></div>\r\n                        <div class=\"navigation-next swiper-button-next\"></div>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </section>\r\n              <br>\r\n              <section class=\"recruit__sec\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"> \r\n                <div class=\"recruit__message\">\r\n                  <div class=\"recruit__valueTitleBox\"><span class=\"c-decorativeSmallTitle-blue recruit__valueTItle-en\">MESSAGE</span>\r\n                    <h3 class=\"recruit__valueTitle-second\">採用担当者より</h3>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <figure class=\"recruit__messagePic\"><img src=\"../_assets/images/lower/recruit/recruit_message.jpg\" alt=\"経営管理本部 人事総務部\"></figure>\r\n                  <p class=\"solution__messImgText\">経営管理本部 <br class=\"u-spDb\">人事総務部<span class=\"solution__messImgName\">採用担当チーム</span></p>\r\n                  <div class=\"recruit__messageTextBox\">\r\n                    <p class=\"recruit__messageTitle\"> 環境を通じた壮大なフィールドで<br class=\"u-spDb\">新たな挑戦の第一歩を</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"recruit__messageText\">SDGsやサステナビリティという言葉が世の中に浸透する以前から、循環型社会の実現に向けて廃棄物の資源化やエネルギーの利活用にひたむきに取り組んできました。培ってきた技術と誇りを胸に、新しい価値を生み出すエンジニアリング会社としてこれからも発展させていきます。</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"recruit__messageText\">いま、テクノロジーの進化は私たちの日常生活をも変えつつあります。一方で機械では代替できない職人の技能や既存の枠に捉われない柔軟な発想、人同士のつながりが生む信頼・安心への価値が再評価されるなど、急速な変化の中で、これからはますます本質的な力が求められます。</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"recruit__messageText\">このような時代にこそ、チームを大切にし、助け合う当社の社風が活きてくるはずです。チャレンジ精神を重んじ、失敗を許容する社風が活きてくるはずです。<br>経験したことのない新しい課題が日々生まれていますが、未知の領域に踏み出す勇気を私たちは称賛します。</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"recruit__messageText\">環境問題や地域課題という壮大なフィールドがあなたを待っています。<br>持続可能な社会のために、新しい一歩を当社で踏み出してみませんか。</p>\r\n                    <p class=\"recruit__messageText recruit__messageText2\">新卒採用について<br>弊社では、入社意欲の高い学生・元気な学生を随時募集しています。<br>その年度のリクルート期間を経過していたとしても、なお弊社を志望頂ける学生については、<br class=\"u-pcDb\">いつでも採用選考を実施しますので、奮ってご応募ください。</p>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </section>\r\n              <div class=\"project__jobBox\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"> \r\n                <div class=\"project__jobContent\">\r\n                  <div class=\"project__jobTitleBox\">\r\n                    <h3 class=\"project__jobTitle\">募集要項</h3>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <div class=\"project__jobItemList\"> \r\n                      <a class=\"project__jobItem\" href=\"../recruit/graduate/\">\r\n                      <p class=\"project__jobItemText\">新卒採用</p></a>\r\n                      <a class=\"project__jobItem\" href=\"../recruit/career/\">\r\n                      <p class=\"project__jobItemText\">キャリア採用</p></a>\r\n                      <a class=\"project__jobItem\" href=\"../recruit/plant/\">\r\n                      <p class=\"project__jobItemText\">事業所採用</p></a>\r\n                  </div>\r\n\r\n                  <div class=\"project__jobEnterBtnmynavi4\">\r\n                    <a href=\"https://job.mynavi.jp/27/pc/corpinfo/displayRecruitingCourseList/index/?corpId=277273\"target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../_assets/images/lower/recruit/recruit_mynavi_logo_2027.png\" alt=\"ホーム\"\"alt=\"マイナビ2027\" border:0;\"></a>\r\n                  </div>\r\n\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"project__jobEnterBtnWrap\">\r\n                  <div class=\"project__jobEnterBtnBox\"><a class=\"project__jobEnterBtn\" href=\"../recruit_form/\">\r\n                      <div class=\"project__jobEnterBtnTextBox\"> \r\n                        <div class=\"project__jobEnterBtnTitle\">エントリーはこちらから</div>\r\n                        <p class=\"project__jobEnterBtnText\">採用に関するお問い合せ・応募はこちら</p>\r\n                        <div class=\"project__jobEnterBtnHeading-sp c-decorativeSmallTitle-whiteTranparent\">ENTRY</div>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div class=\"project__jobEnterBtnHeadingBox\"> \r\n                        <div class=\"project__jobEnterBtnHeading c-decorativeSmallTitle-whiteTranparent\">ENTRY</div>\r\n                      </div></a></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"project__jobEnterBtnWrap\">\r\n                  <div class=\"project__jobEnterBtnBox u-skyBlue\"><a class=\"project__jobEnterBtn\" href=\"../recruit/faq\">\r\n                      <div class=\"project__jobEnterBtnTextBox u-second\">\r\n                        <div class=\"project__jobEnterBtnTitle02\">よくある質問はこちら</div>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div class=\"project__jobEnterBtnHeadingBox\"> \r\n                        <div class=\"project__jobEnterBtnHeading u-second\">Q & A</div>\r\n                      </div></a></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"c-banner\"> \r\n                  <div class=\"c-banner__wrap\"> <a class=\"c-banner__btnBox\" href=\"https://www.jfe-eng.co.jp/news/2023/20230627.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"> <span class=\"c-banner__btn\">月島機械株式会社との国内水エンジニア<br class=\"u-spDb\">リング事業統合に関するお知らせ</span></a></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </main>\r\n    <footer class=\"siteFooter\">\r\n      <div class=\"siteFoote